snippet.title: One Military Camp - Official Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description: One Military Camp is available now in Early Access. Watch the trailer for another look at this base-building military management sim to see gameplay and more. In One Military Camp, train a group of brave misfits into soldiers and embark on a mission to defeat the evil Dragan.
